{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"732","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"走出象牙塔！教育部USR計畫第2期 接軌SDGs列審查要件","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-07-07&nbsp; 12:49&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>聯合報<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>記者章凱閎<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>台北即時報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/USR.JPG' style='width: 800px; height: 468px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>教育部鼓勵大學走出象牙塔，補助大學實踐社會責任（<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>）。教育部表示，第二期（<span lang='EN-US'>109</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>111</span>年）計畫，把接軌「聯合國永續發展目標」（<span lang='EN-US'>SDGs</span>）列為計畫審查要件，引導大學與世界接軌、增進國際能見度，共計核定<span lang='EN-US'>97</span>所大專校院共<span lang='EN-US'>217</span>件計畫。報系資料照</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>教育部鼓勵大學走出象牙塔，補助大學實踐社會責任（<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>）。教育部表示，第二期（<span lang='EN-US'>109</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>111</span>年）計畫，把接軌「聯合國永續發展目標」（<span lang='EN-US'>SDGs</span>）列為計畫審查要件，引導大學與世界接軌、增進國際能見度，共計核定<span lang='EN-US'>97</span>所大專校院共<span lang='EN-US'>217</span>件計畫。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>教育部高教深耕計畫，首度設置「大學社會責任實踐計畫」，以每案一年最高一千萬元、兩年為一期，補助大學成為社會創新的智庫。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>教育部近日公布第二期核定計畫，且為引導大學投入國際場域，各大學<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>計畫皆要連結與屬性相近的<span lang='EN-US'>17</span>項<span lang='EN-US'>SDGs</span>指標，例如「消除貧窮」、「糧食安全」、「高品質教育」、「兩性平等」、「永續能源」等。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>例如台科大<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>計畫「無國界行動工程師培育」，連結<span lang='EN-US'>SDGs</span>的「永續城市與社區」指標。國際師生團隊投入印尼、越南偏鄉，透過實作改善社區基礎設施，培育新一代優質工程師，進而達到居住永續安全、學校永續教育、社區永續發展的目標。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>中央大學<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>計畫「桃海三生－型塑桃園海岸環境與人文發展永續共生」，則連結「因應氣候變遷行動」指標連結，解決桃園海岸面臨環境保護與經濟開發的兩難，讓海岸環境與社區永續，引導青年回流創業生根，推動地方創生。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>台大日前也公布該校首本<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>報告書。校長管中閔表示，該校<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>計畫涵括醫療研究、公共衛生、食品安全、食農教育、長照服務、智慧城市、能源轉型等領域。台大也深入全台各地，甚至是東南亞、非洲等地，例如公衛學院學生遠赴非洲馬拉威，研究瘧疾；台大醫院團隊協助降低南美洲瓜地馬拉新生兒疫病感染率。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>教育部表示，<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>計畫邁入第二期，「接軌<span lang='EN-US'>SDGs</span>指標」也被列為計畫審查要件之一，以引導大學與世界對接，培養具國際視野及移動力的人才。<span lang='EN-US'>USR</span>第二期計畫共計核定<span lang='EN-US'>97</span>所大專院校<span lang='EN-US'>217</span>件計畫。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/6885/4684099</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph'>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-07-09","clk_count":"173"}},"__N_SSG":true}